snippet.title: Metaphor: ReFantazio — Travel Beyond Fantasy | Xbox Series X|S, Windows PC
snippet.description:
More public support, bigger face on the rock. ⛰️

Travel around the United Kingdom of Euchronia, secure the trust of the citizens, and take down rival candidates competing for the throne!

The Royal Tournament begins October 11th, 2024:
Xbox - https://atlus.link/Xbox-Metaphor 
PlayStation - https://atlus.link/PS-Metaphor 
Steam/PC - https://atlus.link/Steam-Metaphor 
Physical - https://atlus.link/Metaphor-Pre-Order
